Module com.example.project3
Package com.example.project3

Class AccountDatabase

java.lang.Object
com.example.project3.AccountDatabase
public class AccountDatabase
extends java.lang.Object
This is an array based container database for accounts with all the different types of accounts. This class also prints all the accounts depending on the order inputted by the user. The array does not shrink but increases in size by 4 when it is full.
Author:
Sebastian Carrasco, Rachael Chin
